Your maternal grandfather is Prophet Muhammad (pbuh),

TU HAI MASIHA-E-JAHAAN SHAAHE KHURASAAN HAI LAQAB YU HAR FARISHTA ROZ PAR AATAA HAI TERE BA ADAB HAAN RAD NAHI HOTI TERE ROZE PE KOI BHI DUA, NANA NABI DADA ALI DADI TERI KHAIRUN NISAA
